Tyra Vaughn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tyra_Vaughn 0 Tyra Vaughn (March 13, 1923 - August 9, 2015) was an American actress who appeared in motion pictures and television throughout the 1940s and late 1950s, who later found a second career as a professional dance instructor.
